'''[[挪威|挪威]]国旗'''由靛藍色[[十字架|十字架]]加上白色邊和周围的红色组成。在白色十字中加入藍色十字，於是誕生了三种颜色的國旗。其中红白蓝三色象徵[[自由|自由]]與[[獨立|獨立]]。

== 设计 ==
{|class="wikitable"
! 绘制方法
! 标准
|-
|[[File:Flag_of_Norway_with_proportions.svg|220px]]<br><center><small>民用旗</small></center><br>[[File:Flag_of_Norway,_state_with_proportions.svg|263px]]<br><center><small>政府旗與軍旗</small></center>
|
* 挪威民用国旗的长宽比为22:16，各颜色的水平分布比例为 6:1:2:1:12，纵向分布比例为 6:1:2:1:6。
* 挪威政府旗的长宽比为27:16，各颜色的水平分布比例为 6:1:2:1:6:11，纵向分布比例为 6:1:2:1:6。

* 色彩以[[Pantone|彩通]]表示，红色为PMS 200，蓝色为PMS 281。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.norden.org/en/information/norwegian-flag |title=The Norwegian flag {{!}} Nordic cooperation |access-date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211009231257/https://www.norden.org/en/information/norwegian-flag |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 以RGB表示的近似值为红色为#BA0C2F，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.pantone.com/color-finder/200-C |title=PANTONE® 200 C - Find a Pantone Color {{!}} Quick Online Color Tool {{!}} Pantone |access-date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716005916/https://www.pantone.com/color-finder/200-C |dead-url=no }}</ref>蓝色为#00205B。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.pantone.com/color-finder/281-C |title=PANTONE® 281 C - Find a Pantone Color {{!}} Quick Online Color Tool {{!}} Pantone |access-date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716084210/https://www.pantone.com/color-finder/281-C |dead-url=no }}</ref>
|}

